name: 🚀 DarkSpace Contribution
description: Propose something new for The DarkSpace
title: "[DarkSpace]: "
labels: ["contribution"]
body:

  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        👋 Welcome, explorer.

        You are about to submit a transmission into **The DarkSpace**.
        Please describe what you would like to add to this mysterious repository.

        (Yes, recipes are acceptable payloads.)

  - type: dropdown
    id: contribution-type
    attributes:
      label: 🛰️ What type of contribution is this?
      description: Select the nature of your incoming transmission
      options:
        - Documentation
        - Recipe
        - Survival Guide
        - Lore
        - Checklist
        - Inspirational Quote
        - Something That Should Definitely Not Be In Space
        - Other
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: description
    attributes:
      label: 🌠 Describe your contribution
      description: Tell us what you're planning to add to The DarkSpace
      placeholder: Example - A guide for making grilled cheese in zero gravity
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: dropdown
    id: urgency
    attributes:
      label: ⏱️ Urgency Level
      description: How urgently is this needed for space operations?
      options:
        - Critical (Crew morale depends on this)
        - High (Useful for long missions)
        - Medium (Nice to have)
        - Low (For vibes only)

  - type: textarea
    id: additional-context
    attributes:
      label: 🪐 Additional Context
      description: Anything else the DarkSpace maintainers should know?
      placeholder: This may or may not involve tacos

  - type: checkboxes
    id: checklist
    attributes:
      label: ✅ Pre-Launch Checklist
      options:
        - label: I have verified this content will not anger the void
        - label: I understand my PR may be reviewed by space pirates
        - label: I am prepared to fork responsibly
